description: Returns a list of proactive resource evaluations.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: Returns a ResourceEvaluationFilters object. EvaluationMode (string) --- Filters all resource evaluations results based on an evaluation mode. TimeWindow (dict) --- Returns a TimeWindow object. StartTime (datetime) --- The start time of an execution. EndTime (datetime) --- The end time of an execution. The end time must be after the start date. EvaluationContextIdentifier (string) --- Filters evaluations for a given infrastructure deployment. For example: CFN Stack.

nested_items.name: EvaluationMode
nested_items.description: The mode of an evaluation. The valid values are Detective or Proactive.

nested_items.name: EvaluationStartTimestamp
nested_items.description: The starting time of an execution.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The nextToken string returned on a previous page that you use to get the next page of results in a paginated response.
